README
======

This is the console server. It parses ANSI compatible escape sequences
and supports multiple virtual consoles. You can in fact have different
resolutions on your virtual consoles, and even mix text and graphical
one -- the console server will have no problems handling this.

-- Per Lundberg <per@chaosdev.io>  Fri, 23 Jun 2000 11:07:58 +0200
